title: The Gavin McInnes Show 2016-09-14
description: Today on TGMS, Gavin can't get enough of Harlem Shake Hillary, questions gentrification, and gets sickened by a question asked to Chelsea Clinton. Charles Johnson comes in studio to discuss Air BnB. Benjamin Moseley Skypes in from the road to talk about trucking regulations. James Blonde aka Johnny Bizarre is in studio next and he talks about sideshows before nailing a nail into his nose and then his penis
